    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概览</h2><strong>你的子弹就是我的子弹！</strong><br>击中或避免它取决于您。<br>独特的Shmup“<strong>Return Ace</strong>”，规则反转，从正面以弹幕击中敌人的军队和Boss。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/8a3c87b33f45168f0bab1e92542c2e3e.poster.avif?t=1647950218\" width=158 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/8a3c87b33f45168f0bab1e92542c2e3e.webm?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/8a3c87b33f45168f0bab1e92542c2e3e.mp4?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>等我醒来的时候，情况已经定了。<br>给予的既不是全部的力量，也不是强壮的身体。<br>它是“<u>回报</u>”一切的力量。<br>战斗开始了，在某人的声音引导下，甚至没有确定他的身份和愿望。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/131f4dd4622524364f4f61465c6fd94f.poster.avif?t=1647950218\" width=158 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/131f4dd4622524364f4f61465c6fd94f.webm?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/131f4dd4622524364f4f61465c6fd94f.mp4?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我们采用了独特的游戏系统，因为我们的目标是玩不太可能的 Shmup。<br>主角拥有以下能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/d5e443cebc80e6dbb4bd79660f8c5abc.webp?t=1647950218\" width=40 height=40 /></span><strong>&quot;Absorb&quot;</strong><br>吸收、登记和击退敌人能量子弹的基本能力。<br>因为它储存了射击的能量，所以被击中是必不可少的，也是各种攻击的起点。<br>请注意，如果您超过允许的量，它会过热并变得毫无防备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/ed9eb0064360608820c52aed065b87b3.webp?t=1647950218\" width=40 height=40 /></span><strong>&quot;Hacking&quot;</strong><br>能够破解敌机并将它们翻过来。<br>只对空中的敌人和物理引导的子弹有效，它消耗大量能量但可以在瞬间成为盟友。<br>适合对付麻烦的敌人和防御物理引导的子弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/31bed5945017b6fa050d4bb450d19311.webp?t=1647950218\" width=40 height=40 /></span><strong>&quot;Rolling&quot;</strong><br>暂时变得无敌并从物理接触（包括物理弹药）中反弹的能力。<br>能量弹被飞行器的动能抵消，射击在使用过程中成为强化弹。<br>要小心，因为它很容易被高功率能量子弹和持续接触的能量子弹所迷惑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/e1bac3b6775d2b631fea93e28ec32f7b.poster.avif?t=1647950218\" width=182 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/e1bac3b6775d2b631fea93e28ec32f7b.webm?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/e1bac3b6775d2b631fea93e28ec32f7b.mp4?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/beea353cc8524b2cdc3ae5857e23b294.poster.avif?t=1647950218\" width=182 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/beea353cc8524b2cdc3ae5857e23b294.webm?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/beea353cc8524b2cdc3ae5857e23b294.mp4?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有四个难度级别：Full Tune Up (Level1)、Prototype (Level2)、Wanted (Level3) 和 World Ruler (LevelMAX)。<br>每个都有不同的故事、BGM 安排、飞机能力、敌人力量和战斗程序。<br>您可以随时更改难度级别，除非通关分数得到确认。<br>该故事还配备了自动和跳过功能，因此您可以专注于Shmup部分。<br><br>显示通关游戏时获得的标题。<br>标题可以通过在任何难度级别进行游戏来获得，除了隐藏级别。<br>标题具有适合内容的有用能力，如果您收集它，您可以显着增强自己的机器。<br>得分高且难度高的标题具有重新思考游戏本身的强大能力。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/3633412101e2e2df9cc6ea9e691d79a7.poster.avif?t=1647950218\" width=158 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/3633412101e2e2df9cc6ea9e691d79a7.webm?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/3633412101e2e2df9cc6ea9e691d79a7.mp4?t=1647950218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 记录能量为0%时吸收的子弹。<br>如果您想使用另一颗子弹，请避免吸收并通过射击、砍杀和滚动来消耗它。<br>- 能量子弹具有功率、能量效率、射程和强度关系等多种要素。<br>强化效果不一样，请尽量找到自己喜欢的。<br>- 键绑定可以在配置中完成。<br>本游戏使用射击、吸收、砍杀、滚动和4个按键，操作非常多。<br>建议使用舒适的设置进行游戏。<br>- 你也可以使用滚动攻击boss。当你黑进老板...？<br><br>- 试用版最多有2个阶段，标题增强已被削减。<br>Wanted（Level3）World Ruler（LevelMAX）有严格的难度级别。<br>请体验它作为一个未加强的水平。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作方法</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873770/extras/ffdf783d4cb9c3b0ce857cf2d3af8f67.avif?t=1647950218\" width=400 height=250 /></span><br>1：射击（决定） 默认键：<strong>左 Shift 键</strong> 固定键：<strong>Enter 键</strong><br>2：吸收（决定） 默认键：<strong>Z</strong> 固定键：<strong>右 Ctrl 键</strong><br>3：黑客（取消） 默认键：<strong>X</strong> 固定键：<strong>BackSpace 键</strong><br>4：旋转（取消） 默认键：<strong>C</strong> 固定键：<strong>右 Shift 键</strong><br>红、黄：固定功能<br>蓝色：可变功能",
